text: Winchell's Donuts is an international doughnut company and coffeehouse chain. It was founded by Verne Winchell on October 8, 1948, in Temple City, California. It has 170 stores in 6 western states, as well as Guam, Saipan, and Saudi Arabia. It is headquartered in the City of Industry, California.
